    - target: {fileID: 846471609284694202, guid: 4c5f1da3e5bb7b0469e905f6fe813a98, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: A chandelier composed entirely of maybe drifted past the staircase,
        offering coupons for underwater bicycles, while the carpet practiced ballet
        in a language made of parentheses. In the distance, an encyclopedia blinked
        twice, forgot how to be an encyclopedia, and became a very determined potato
        with opinions about jazz lizards.
